{"type": "article", "id": 28645, "title": "户外家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-24T06:50:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702161710vm5IEBlX4SnqGHF8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>设计师 <a href=\"http://www.stephenburksmanmade.com/\">Stephen Burks</a> 曾在 2015 年为 <a href=\"http://www.roche-bobois.com/en-US\">Roche Bobois</a> 四十周年设计了一套名为 Traveler 的户外家具，其中包括了两款色彩鲜艳的扶手椅。在系列的新品中，Burks 把管状的喷漆钢结构同五颜六色的灯芯绒靠垫结合在了一起，并且以印尼手工艺为灵感设计了两套不同的配色，为这个系列注入了一股亚洲风情。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161706DVYQZjH0b4lpe5zG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161707ZyRLDepqrlUiQx3E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161707jm2p6qek384CEVdX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021617086flUzZgJFQnsXLvR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}